<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Westfield | Studio de Jeux Roblox</title>
    <style>
        /* Styles Généraux */
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-style: border-box;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            background-color: #0f1115;
            color: #f5f6fa;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        /* Barre de Navigation */
        header {
            background-color: #161a23;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 1000;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #ff4757;
        }

        .navbar {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 1rem 5%;
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .logo {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #fff;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
        }

        .logo span {
            color: #ff4757;
        }

        .nav-links {
            list-style: none;
            display: flex;
            gap: 2rem;
        }

        .nav-links a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #a4b0be;
            font-weight: 500;
            transition: color 0.3s;
        }

        .nav-links a:hover {
            color: #ff4757;
        }

        /* Section Accueil (Hero) */
        .hero {
            background: linear-gradient(rgba(15, 17, 21, 0.8), rgba(15, 17, 21, 0.95)), url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1511512578047-dfb367046420?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1350&q=80') no-repeat center center/cover;
            height: 75vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            text-align: center;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 0 1rem;
        }

        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 3.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            text-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(255, 71, 87, 0.4);
        }

        .hero p {
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            max-width: 650px;
            color: #ced6e0;
        }

        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #ff4757;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 0.8rem 2.5rem;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(255, 71, 87, 0.4);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .btn:hover {
            background-color: #ff6b81;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(255, 71, 87, 0.6);
        }

        /* Container de section */
        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 5rem auto;
            padding: 0 5%;
        }

        .section-title {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
            font-size: 2.2rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

        .section-title span {
            color: #ff4757;
        }

        /* Section Nos Jeux */
        .grid-jeux {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(320px, 1fr));
            gap: 2.5rem;
        }

        .game-card {
            background: #1e222b;
            border-radius: 12px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
            transition: transform 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s;
            border: 1px solid #2f3542;
        }

        .game-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-8px);
            box-shadow: 0 15px 30px rgba(255, 71, 87, 0.2);
            border-color: #ff4757;
        }

        .game-img {
            height: 220px;
            background-color: #2f3542;
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
        }

        .game-content {
            padding: 1.8rem;
        }

        .game-content h3 {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
            color: #fff;
        }

        .game-content p {
            color: #a4b0be;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            height: 60px;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .btn-play {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #2ed573;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 0.6rem 1.5rem;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            transition: background 0.2s;
        }

        .btn-play:hover {
            background-color: #26af5f;
        }

        /* Section Crédits / Équipe */
        .grid-credits {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
            gap: 2rem;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .member-card {
            background: #161a23;
            padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
            border-radius: 10px;
            text-align: center;
            border: 1px solid #2f3542;
            transition: border-color 0.3s;
        }

        .member-card:hover {
            border-color: #ff4757;
        }

        .avatar {
            width: 100px;
            height: 100px;
            background-color: #2f3542;
            border-radius: 50%;
            margin: 0 auto 1.5rem;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            color: #ff4757;
            border: 3px solid #ff4757;
        }

        .member-card h4 {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
        }

        .member-card p {
            color: #ff4757;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

        /* Pied de page */
        footer {
            background-color: #0b0c10;
            color: #a4b0be;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 3rem 1rem;
            margin-top: 5rem;
            border-top: 1px solid #1e222b;
        }

        footer p {
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        footer span {
            color: #ff4757;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header>
        <nav class="navbar">
            <div class="logo">West<span>field</span></div>
            <ul class="nav-links">
                <li><a href="#accueil">Accueil</a></li>
                <li><a href="#jeux">Nos Jeux</a></li>
                <li><a href="#credits">Crédits</a></li>
            </ul>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <section id="accueil" class="hero">
        <h1>Créateurs d'univers Roblox</h1>
        <p>Nous concevons des expériences uniques, immersives et amusantes pour la communauté Roblox. Plongez dans nos créations dès aujourd'hui !</p>
        <a href="#jeux" class="btn">Voir les Jeux</a>
    </section>

    <section id="jeux" class="container">
        <h2 class="section-title">Nos <span>Jeux</span></h2>
        <div class="grid-jeux">
            
            <div class="game-card">
                <div class="game-img" style="background-image: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1542751371-adc38448a05e?auto=format&fit=crop&w=600&q=80');"></div>
                <div class="game-content">
                    <h3>Westfield RP</h3>
                    <p>Incarnez le rôle de votre choix dans une ville ultra réaliste. Conduisez, travaillez et rencontrez des amis !</p>
                    <a href="https://www.roblox.com" target="_blank" class="btn-play">Rejoindre sur Roblox</a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="game-card">
                <div class="game-img" style="background-image: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1552820728-8b83bb6b773f?auto=format&fit=crop&w=600&q=80');"></div>
                <div class="game-content">
                    <h3>Survival Challenge</h3>
                    <p>Un jeu de survie intense où l'esprit d'équipe et vos réflexes seront vos seules armes pour survivre.</p>
                    <a href="https://www.roblox.com" target="_blank" class="btn-play">Rejoindre sur Roblox</a>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="credits" class="container">
        <h2 class="section-title">Les <span>Crédits</span></h2>
        <div class="grid-credits">
            
            <div class="member-card">
                <div class="avatar">👑</div>
                <h4>mael354</h4>
                <p>Fondateur / Dev Principal</p>
            </div>

            <div class="member-card">
                <div class="avatar">🛠️</div>
                <h4>Alex</h4>
                <p>Builder / Modeleur 3D</p>
            </div>

            <div class="member-card">
                <div class="avatar">🎨</div>
                <h4>Sarah</h4>
                <p>Graphiste / UI Designer</p>
            </div>

        </div>
    </section>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2026 <span>Westfield Roblox</span>. Tous droits réservés.</p>
        <p style="font-size: 0.8rem; color: #57606f;">Ce site n'est pas affilié directement à Roblox Corporation.</p>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
